## Feature Comparison

### Before vs After

#### ProfileSettingsPage
| Feature | Before | After |
|---------|--------|-------|
| Password Validation | Basic | Advanced with requirements |
| Confirm Password | No | Yes, with match indicator |
| Password Strength | None | Visual indicator + checklist |
| Form Validation | None | Real-time with error messages |
| Field Indicators | None | Required/Optional labels |
| Helpful Info | None | Tips section with icon |
| Alerts | Basic icon prop | Proper component usage |

#### UserProfilePage
| Feature | Before | After |
|---------|--------|-------|
| Layout | Single column | 3-column responsive |
| Stats | Inline only | Dedicated sidebar cards |
| Profile Status | None | Visual progress tracker |
| Quick Info | None | Quick stats card |
| Responsiveness | Basic | Mobile-optimized |

#### UserProfileHeader
| Feature | Before | After |
|---------|--------|-------|
| Background | Plain surface | Gradient |
| Avatar | Simple circle | Status badge included |
| Visual Hierarchy | Flat | Better layering |
| Stats Layout | Horizontal | Grid-based |
| Status Display | None | Active indicator |

